cat > .gitignore << 'EOF'
## .NET Core
bin/
obj/
*.user
*.userosscache
*.csproj.user
*.swp
*.suo
*.sln.docstates

## Build results
[Dd]ebug/
[Dd]ebugPublic/
[Rr]elease/
[Rr]eleases/
x64/
x86/
build/
bld/
[Bb]in/
[Oo]bj/

## Visual Studio
.vs/
.vscode/
*.sln.ide
*.sln.args

## User-specific files
*.rsuser
*.suo
*.user
*.userosscache
*.sln.docstates

## dotnet tools
tools/
*.dotnet

## Logs
logs/
*.log
*.lognunit.xml

## Coverage files
*.coverage
*.coverage.xml
*.dotCover
*.trx

## Windows image file caches
Thumbs.db
ehthumbs.db

## macOS
.DS_Store
__pycache__/
*.pyc
EOF